    - '#^Call to method register\(\) on an unknown class Whoops\\Run\.$#'
    - '#^Parameter \$handler of method Rougin\\Slytherin\\Debug\\WhoopsErrorHandler\:\:setHandler\(\) has invalid type Whoops\\Handler\\HandlerInterface\.$#'
    - '#^Call to method pushHandler\(\) on an unknown class Whoops\\Run\.$#'
    - '#^Instantiated class Zend\\Diactoros\\Response not found\.$#'
    - '#^Property Rougin\\Slytherin\\Middleware\\StratigilityDispatcher\:\:\$zend has unknown class Zend\\Stratigility\\MiddlewarePipe as its type\.$#'
    - '#^Parameter \$pipe of method Rougin\\Slytherin\\Middleware\\StratigilityDispatcher\:\:__construct\(\) has invalid type Zend\\Stratigility\\MiddlewarePipe\.$#'
