    - '#^PHPDoc tag @var contains unknown class Twig\\Environment\.$#'
    - '#^Property Rougin\\Slytherin\\Template\\TwigRenderer\:\:\$twig has unknown class Twig\\Environment as its type\.$#'
    - '#^Parameter \$twig of method Rougin\\Slytherin\\Template\\TwigRenderer\:\:__construct\(\) has invalid type Twig\\Environment\.$#'
    - '#^Call to method addGlobal\(\) on an unknown class Twig\\Environment\.$#'
